y\": \"No extra Maven dependency or Docker image is needed: parquet-jackson 1.16.0 is a shaded Jackson bundle with jackson-core/databind/annotations 2.19.2 relocated under shaded.parquet.com.fasterxml.jackson. However, tests that exercise Jackson's EnumSet/EnumMap enum-type discovery need a JVM module opening.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Use the shaded APIs from shaded.parquet.com.fasterxml.jackson.*. If tests exercise ClassUtil.findEnumType on EnumSet or EnumMap, keep/add JVM and native-image build arguments: --add-opens=java.base/java.util=ALL-UNNAMED.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The reported failure appears to be a Jackson behavior/assertion mismatch for enum annotation introspection rather than missing dependency or service setup.\",\n    \"Adding unshaded com.fasterxml.jackson dependencies would bypass the artifact under test and should be avoided unless a test intentionally compares behavior.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c0b7409e78d120f016a3f6c9d8bfc819582d6bb560e66698f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 532, "output": 738, "cacheRead": 32768, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34038, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782541458209, "responseId": "resp_0c0b7409e78d120f016a3f6c92f5308195a8548177b491fb00"}}
